{Name}{}{Woman patron}
{DescAliveShort}{}{You see a woman patron.}
{DescAliveFull}{}{This woman feels here like at home.}
{Speech 1}{}{Initial preferences}
{Speech 1 Answer 2}{}{-}
{Speech 1 Answer 5}{}{-}
{Speech 1 Answer 7}{}{-}
{Speech 2}{}{Hello! Nice to see new faces in here. Maybe you'll buy me a drink?}
{Speech 2 Answer 3}{}{Sure, why not? Let's drink something! [You pay 2 chips]}
{Speech 2 Answer Exit}{}{Maybe next time.@@Sorry, I have no mood to chat right now.}
{Speech 3}{}{Thank you! You're a nice guy!}
{Speech 3 Answer 4}{}{Yes, I am. Would you like one more drink?  [You pay 2 chips] Tell me what's going on here?}
{Speech 3 Answer Exit}{}{Sorry, gotta go!}
{Speech 4}{}{Our town hasn't really changed a lot for few years. Since Metzger and his dogs have been banished from the town nobody is afraid to become a slave. Still we have problems with junkies and drunkards. Morever, today there are even more bootleggers and drug dealers in the town, so the problem's become even worse. But that doesn't really matter, lately some shady men appeared in the town so it's impossible to go out without being robbed out of your pockets. So keep your eyes open!}
{Speech 4 Answer Exit}{}{Thanks for the information!}
{Speech 5}{}{Oh, it's you @pname@! Nice to see you!}
{Speech 5 Answer 6}{}{Hello! What's new?}
{Speech 5 Answer 3}{}{Would you like to have a drink for our friendship? [You pay 2 chips]}
{Speech 5 Answer Exit}{}{See you later.@@Hello, sorry gotta go now!@@Oh, that's you! May I ask you where the restroom is?}
{Speech 6}{}{Nothing new. Maybe you'd like to join me?@@I'm here for a long time and everything is still as it used to be.}
{Speech 6 Answer Exit}{}{I see. Next time!}
{Speech 7}{}{[You see a woman in the bar. She smiles at you]  Oh, new face here! Maybe you'll buy me a drink for the acquaintance.}
{Speech 7 Answer 8}{}{Yeah, drink! [She takes 2 chips from your wallet]}
{Speech 7 Answer 9}{}{Erm...@@Wow.@@Argh!@@Ummm!}
{Speech 8}{}{You're a nice boy! Ok, now go somewhere else.}
{Speech 8 Answer Exit}{}{Ok.}
{Speech 9}{}{You don't seem to be healthy.}
{Speech 9 Answer Exit}{}{Nah!}
